<div class="grid_12">
  <p>
    Choose a collection to work with.  If you have &quot;write&quot; access to
    a collection, you can add new objects or update existing objects.  Contact
    UC3 if you don't see the collection you need.  Whatever else we need to say.
  </p>

  <p>
    We really don't know what is happening with the profile service right
    now, so we're not sure how permissions or number of objects will ever
    get populated.
  </p>

  <h3>Collections</h3>

  <%= @grps.inspect %>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 40%;">Collection</th>
        <th style="width: 20%;">Permissions</th>
        <th style="width: 20%;"># Objects</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @grps.each do |grp| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= grp.description %></td>
        <td><%= grp.permission %></td>
        <td><%= grp.object_count %></td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
